                Mr. Ronald Chamberlain
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dd08fd87-e4ee-45c8-b99e-b5babf0851c6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
