            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ad323506-ea29-4969-bf3d-f05c007c4412">
                Mr. H. Wilson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ad323506-ea29-4969-bf3d-f05c007c4412" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-03-17/debates/bcdbbcb4-a301-4087-8f93-9a768488bd7c/HosieryRepairNeedles(Imports)#contribution-ad323506-ea29-4969-bf3d-f05c007c4412">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am not prepared to prohibit the importation of these needles. Prohibition could not be justified on balance of payments grounds. It would also lead to suspension of manufacture of machines of which the needles form a small but indispensable part.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ad323506-ea29-4969-bf3d-f05c007c4412" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-03-17/debates/bcdbbcb4-a301-4087-8f93-9a768488bd7c/HosieryRepairNeedles(Imports)#contribution-ad323506-ea29-4969-bf3d-f05c007c4412">
